data.description: Beautiful nature setting with panoramic mountain views!    Welcome to your private oasis nestled on a serene cul-de-sac backing to a mountain preserve for ultimate privacy. Complete with 4 bedrooms/2.5 baths, 1.25 acres of land, workshop, fish pond, see-through fireplace, and desert landscaping.  Tranquility awaits in the backyard-covered patio. Mature trees, walkways, and a variety of fruit trees are part of this beautiful yard.   The spacious kitchen features a tile backsplash, tile floors, a formal dining area, and an extra room for a pantry.  The master bedroom provides direct backyard access and has a recently renovated bathroom with dual vanity and tile surroundings. The additional bedrooms and full bath are conveniently located on opposing sides from the master bedroom.   MORE.... Many features and extras included which are ceramic tile/laminate floors, dual pane windows, chain link fence, motion-sensor security lights, timer irrigation system, metal underlay gutters, recently upgraded sliders, recently replaced all toilets, smart lock key doors, three-stage Pelican System water softener, and more.  Less than a minute to restaurants, shops, and easy access from the freeway.   A lifestyle of serenity and convenience awaits!
